event.title: FSFE Berlin group meeting in Berlin, Deutschland

body.p: The Berlin group of FSFE supporters is meeting at Kieztreff Undine (Hagenstra√üe 57 Berlin (S/U Bhf Lichtenberg)) to prepare the events for the rest of the year and chat about current Free Software related topics.
